[SPEAKER_00] možda najvažnija stvar.

707
00:32:20,319 --> 00:32:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] Najvažnija stvar i kad vidim da mi to kopne,

708
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] baš mi onako bilo krive,

709
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] nekog sam poslijeo se stabiliziravati,

710
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] vraćati se,

711
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] znam da je najvažniji osobni odnos s Bogom.

712
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:33,160
[SPEAKER_00] Kada to fali, da je loše.

713
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] I ja prestanem, prestanem malo u aktivizam,

714
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] prestanem to i prestanem drugima pričati o Bogu,

715
00:32:41,019 --> 00:32:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali se bacimo ovaj dio,

716
00:32:42,579 --> 00:32:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] di baš onako se družim s gospodinom.

717
00:32:47,759 --> 00:32:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] Proodim vrijeme s njim,

718
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] razmatram.

719
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i u tom nekom osobnom odnosu s Bogom,

720
00:32:52,859 --> 00:32:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam više s njim,

721
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi je pokazao,

722
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] baš koz jednu situaciju u životu,

723
00:32:58,980 --> 00:33:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] gdje me onako baš ponizio i dokazao mi da zapravo

724
00:33:01,799 --> 00:33:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne trebam ništa pričat.

725
00:33:05,079 --> 00:33:08,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nego, ako mi imamo osobni odnos s Bogom doba,

726
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] onda će naš svaki pokret biti evangelizacija.

727
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će nas sad iskoristiti,

728
00:33:13,539 --> 00:33:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] a od ovog laprdanja, od toga nema ništa.

729
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazim na more, radit,

730
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] i sad između crkva se nalazi,

731
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] meni između dva dućana.

732
00:33:23,359 --> 00:33:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dućani su razmatili dosta,

733
00:33:25,559 --> 00:33:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali crkva, moram tu proći pored crkve.

734
00:33:27,019 --> 00:33:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam tad u osobnom odnosu s Bogom dobar.

735
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ne pričam puno ljudima o Bogu,

736
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] nego nastoji živjeti kako treba.

737
00:33:35,759 --> 00:33:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] I samo da kažem osobni odnos s Bogom,

738
00:33:40,079 --> 00:33:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne smatram to odlazak u crkvu,

739
00:33:42,019 --> 00:33:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] to se podrazumijeva,

740
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] nego ovo drugo.

741
00:33:43,539 --> 00:33:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] I ja tada prolazim 20 puta u danu pored crkve.

742
00:33:49,559 --> 00:33:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] I uvijek napravim jednu malu gestu,

743
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] napravim ovako znak križa,

744
00:33:54,539 --> 00:33:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] ili odem u crkvu i poklonim se.

745
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je bilo što sam ja radio to ljeto.

746
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] I nikome nisam pričao Bogu.

747
00:34:02,599 --> 00:34:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ali te moje neke male geste

748
00:34:05,319 --> 00:34:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] vidio jedan mladić iz jednog kafića,

749
00:34:07,099 --> 00:34:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] i to je njega nekako natjeralo da ode u crkvu.

750
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Otiš on u crkvu,

751
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] normalno kako u tim malim mjestima

752
00:34:14,739 --> 00:34:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] znaš koje sve bakici ide u crkvu,

753
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad se pojavi neko novi,

754
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] odmah ti je onako drago,

755
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] super, još je to bio neki mladić,

756
00:34:21,599 --> 00:34:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja stvarno nisam mislio da ja imam veze s tim.

757
00:34:25,219 --> 00:34:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] dok na kraj ljeta on dolazi do mene,

758
00:34:27,739 --> 00:34:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] onako predstavio mi se i kaže,

759
00:34:30,219 --> 00:34:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] evo samo da ti zahvalim,

760
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] radi onoga što si ti križom

761
00:34:34,739 --> 00:34:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] križio ispred crkve,

762
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:39,800
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam otišao u crkvu,

763
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] i mene je buzila Božja ljubav

764
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam razgovarao danas sa kapelanom i sa župnikom

765
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] i ja ću postati katolički svećenik,

766
00:34:48,500 --> 00:34:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] idem u sjemenište.

767
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mene je to onako baš dotaklo

768
00:34:52,619 --> 00:34:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] i on i je sad katolički svećenik

769
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] i sretno živi svoj poziv.

770
00:34:57,119 --> 00:35:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, tada sam presto puno pričati o Bogu,

771
00:35:01,239 --> 00:35:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] nego nastavimo živjeti u tom nekom osobnom ondosu s Bogom,

772
00:35:05,519 --> 00:35:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] a onda će nas Bog iskoristiti

773
00:35:07,519 --> 00:35:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] za sve što ono što nam treba,

774
00:35:09,519 --> 00:35:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] sluge smo beskorisni.

775
00:35:10,619 --> 00:35:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] Tada kad sam čuo od njega

776
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] da ide za svećenik i tako,

777
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] nakon toga normalno je bilo

778
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] da i ja razmišljam što je za mene,

779
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] što ću ja, koji je moj poziv.

780
00:35:24,739 --> 00:35:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vrlo brzo meni Bog govori

781
00:35:27,619 --> 00:35:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] da je to bračni život,

782
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] da je život sa ženom

783
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] i hvala Bogu,

784
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je svećenik i poziv stvarno jako težak.

785
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da ja tada odlučim,

786
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] ok, to je bračni poziv, dobro,

787
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne znam šta s tim,

788
00:35:41,340 --> 00:35:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] što, Bože,

789
00:35:43,579 --> 00:35:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] i ja imam takav neki odnos s Bogom

790
00:35:45,139 --> 00:35:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] da ja kažem, ok, da, treba bi se ženiti,

791
00:35:48,159 --> 00:35:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali što, kako,

792
00:35:50,099 --> 00:35:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam što napraviti, što,

793
00:35:51,719 --> 00:35:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] evo, krenut ću moliti, pa šta.

794
00:35:53,019 --> 00:35:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] I baš tako,

795
00:35:54,239 --> 00:35:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] krenem moliti,

796
00:35:55,579 --> 00:35:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] krenem moliti,

797
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog mi nekako govori

798
00:35:59,159 --> 00:36:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] kroz vrijeme,

799
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] mi govori

800
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao korake,

801
00:36:04,619 --> 00:36:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] kako se dobro ženiti.

802
00:36:07,559 --> 00:36:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] ja te korake

803
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] slušam.

804
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ispoštujem

805
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] i sretno se ženim.

806
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

807
00:36:13,599 --> 00:36:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

808
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] sad ću ja te korake,

809
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

810
00:36:21,179 --> 00:36:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] evo, kako je to dobro,

811
00:36:22,659 --> 00:36:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] morat ću na pamet korake,

812
00:36:23,719 --> 00:36:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] da sam papir izgubio od koraka,

813
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali dobro,

814
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] nema veze, znam ih na pamet,

815
00:36:28,639 --> 00:36:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa ih,

816
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ja to prošao.

817
00:36:30,039 --> 00:36:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

818
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] evo, daj, mikrova.

819
00:36:32,239 --> 00:36:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ok,

820
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] prva stvar koju mi je Bog stavio na srce,

821
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

822
00:36:39,559 --> 00:36:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] ja vam govorim ovako,

823
00:36:40,699 --> 00:36:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] čisto da neću vas tužit,

824
00:36:42,739 --> 00:36:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] možete ovo i kopirat,

825
00:36:43,719 --> 00:36:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali, evo,

826
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] slobodno uzmite ovo.

827
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi neki korak koji mi je Bog stavio na srce

828
00:36:49,599 --> 00:36:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam ga poslušao je to,

829
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] da molim za ženu.

830
00:36:52,059 --> 00:36:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] I, stop,

831
00:36:53,139 --> 00:36:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je kraj,

832
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, kraj nakane,

833
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] moliti za ženu.

834
00:36:57,340 --> 00:37:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, moliti se majci Božjoj.

835
00:37:00,019 --> 00:37:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio prvi korak.

836
00:37:01,239 --> 00:37:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nekako majka zna što sino treba,

837
00:37:04,519 --> 00:37:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] a i čeri.

838
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:08,659
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi korak,

839
00:37:08,659 --> 00:37:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] jako važan korak,

840
00:37:10,619 --> 00:37:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] na kojem je molitva

841
00:37:12,199 --> 00:37:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] baš odvela do tog koraka,

842
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] a to je obrati pažnje na brakove oko sebe

843
00:37:16,519 --> 00:37:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjet će što želiš.

844
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kada molite za ženu

845
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] i obratite pažnje na brakove oko sebe,

846
00:37:25,099 --> 00:37:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam vrlo brzo vidio,

847
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo sam brzo vidio ono što ne želim.

848
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] To se nekako vrlo brzo pokaže.

849
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo tako puno primjera brakova.

850
00:37:34,219 --> 00:37:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali isto tako,

851
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] ima brakova oko nas koji su onako predivni

852
00:37:39,039 --> 00:37:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] i tu će nam Bog pokazati što želim.

853
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] Tu mi je Bog pokazao što želim.

854
00:37:43,699 --> 00:37:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] I kada sam vidio što želim,

855
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] u tim brakovima

856
00:37:47,619 --> 00:37:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] i kako bih želio da mi žena bude,

857
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] paralelno,

858
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] sam vidio i kakav bi ja muškara

859
00:37:56,059 --> 00:37:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] sreo postati.

860
00:37:56,880 --> 00:38:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što je sve to u tim brakovima

861
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] i onda tu je jako lijepa ovaj sirah 636.

862
00:38:04,159 --> 00:38:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ako vidiš razumna čovjeka,

863
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] rado ga posjeti

864
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] i neka ti stopalo

865
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] oteru njegov prag kuće.

866
00:38:11,559 --> 00:38:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je onako dobro.

867
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kada vidite takav brak,

868
00:38:14,019 --> 00:38:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ja sam nekog postao kao tajni agent.

869
00:38:18,019 --> 00:38:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] dolazio bi tako špio u goste i to.

870
00:38:20,039 --> 00:38:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] I gledao bi što mi se sviđa,

871
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] što mi se ne sviđa

872
00:38:25,199 --> 00:38:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] i kakav bi ja trebao postati

873
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] i kakavu bi ženu trebao tražiti.

874
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tada u tim godinama

875
00:38:30,139 --> 00:38:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] imamo filozofiju svakako o ženama

876
00:38:33,539 --> 00:38:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] i kakvu mi ženu tražimo

877
00:38:35,019 --> 00:38:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] i kakvom bi žena trebala biti

878
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] i šta to.

879
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad obratimo pažnju

880
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] na brakove oko sebe,

881
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo brzo vidimo ono što nam se sviđa.

882
00:38:42,619 --> 00:38:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujte mi, svak od vas zna,

883
00:38:44,719 --> 00:38:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] evo to znam na vlastite kože,

884
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] sam osjetio,

885
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] zna, odmah sam vidio,

886
00:38:48,539 --> 00:38:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ja zapravo znam što želim.

887
00:38:51,119 --> 00:38:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam pogledao tako brakove.

888
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali prvo sam vidio što ne želim.

889
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] Treći korak na koji me je Bog tada odveo

890
00:38:58,780 --> 00:39:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] je kad znaš što želiš,

891
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] moli precizno

892
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] i upiši muža i ženu kako bi htio.

893
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tada kada znam već što bi htio,

894
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] tada ste opasni igračevo,

895
00:39:09,619 --> 00:39:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] tada sam ja postao opasan igrač,

896
00:39:11,039 --> 00:39:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] znam što želim, molim,

897
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] znam kakav bi želio postati,

898
00:39:15,059 --> 00:39:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] znam kakvu ženu hoću

899
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] i tako molim precizno.

900
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] I najvažniji korak,

901
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] četvrti korak,

902
00:39:20,579 --> 00:39:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] bez ova tri koraka ne znači ništa,

903
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] bez četvrto koraka,

904
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] a četvrti korak je pokreni se.

905
00:39:25,059 --> 00:39:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ono, vjerojatno vam neće pokucati na prozor.

906
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:29,880
